bib.title: 196Pt(n,xn yp gamma) reactions using spallation neutrons from E(n)= 1 to 250 MeV

free_txt: Gamma pulse-height spectrum fitted with computer code
Corrected for internal conversion and detector
Not corrected for multiple scattering; estimated to be
15 coaxial Ge detectors. All of the planar detectors
were fitted with NaI nose-cone suppression elements.
obtained by normalizing to GNASH calculations.
Gamma energy calibrated using 65 well-known in-beam
gamma rays identified in 196Pt and other isotopes.
No reply from E. Tavukcu to author proof.
Data received by email from E. Tavukcu, 1 May 2002.
